I had an incredible time playing the Bostonian gangster, David Turner, alongside a very talented cast and crew on the season finale of “History’s Greatest Heists” with the legendary @piercebrosnanofficial 🙏🕵🏻

I was floored to witness how epic the campaign was with billboards on Sunset Blvd and throughout LA. It was exciting to see how warm the reception has been for the show, which now has an 8.4 rating on IMDB. Congratulations to the whole team! What amazing experience it all was! ✨👏

The full season is now streaming on @historytv website!

Today an American dream came true. I received my green card! 

10 years of blood, sweat and tears has culminated to this milestone. My new chapter of freedom begins. I’m overwhelmed with emotions! Wow! 

Here is a carousel post expressing my pure American joy!

God Bless America my home sweet home. 🙏🥹🇺🇸🎊💚

#greencard 
#americandream 
#godblesstheusa

Happy Canadian Thanksgiving to all my loved ones back home! I’m in shock because as I write this I am looking at my Green Card that came in the mail today! What timing!  I’ll be able to travel to Canada again! It’s been over a year!🎊🎉

So much to be thankful for! 🇨🇦🇺🇸

Viggo: That "fuckin' nobody"... is John Wick. He once was an associate of ours. They call him "Baba Yaga."

Iosef: The Boogeyman?

Viggo: Well, John wasn't exactly the Boogeyman. He was the one you sent to kill the fucking Boogeyman.

Iosef: Oh.

Viggo: John is a man of focus, commitment, sheer will... something you know very little about. I once saw him kill three men in a bar... with a pencil, with a fucking pencil.
